data.description: 4.5% ASSUMABLE LOAN OPTION! This updated ranch style home with a finished basement has been meticulously maintained! Upon entering the home, you are greeted with a beautiful custom tile entryway and new luxury vinyl plank throughout the main floor. You will also notice the custom wood accents on the walls throughout the home. Cook like a gourmet chef in the fully equipped and modernized kitchen. This stunning kitchen has new granite countertops, black stainless steel KitchenAid appliances, refinished cabinets, a farmhouse sink, and a dining room with a view. The outdoor space, vast and well-kept, provides a canvas for gardening enthusiasts or those looking to curate their personal oasis. Entertain on the large freshly painted deck or spend time in the greenhouse. Bring your toys, there is additional parking for an RV or a boat! This home's prime location ensures proximity to acclaimed schools, shopping destinations and an array of dining and entertainment options. Close to Glenmere Park, Union Colony Civic Center, Boomerang Links Golf Course, North Colorado Medical Center, and High Plains Library District. West Lake Park is a desirable neighborhood that is centrally located near all the necessities, this one will not last long! Embrace the refined living this home offers, arrange a private viewing and experience the charm firsthand. Option to move the laundry to the main floor. Seller financing/rent to own option also available. NO HOA or Metro Tax!
